Summary:

Cloud computing is the on-demand supply of IT resources over the internet, with pay-as-you-go pricing.

Cloud deployment models:
    1. Cloud-based deployment
    2. On-premises deployment
    3. Hybrid deployment

Cloud computing service models:
    1. IaaS : Infrastructure-as-a-Service
    2. PaaS : Platform-as-a-Service
    3. SaaS : Software-as-a-Service

Benefits of cloud computing:
    1. Pay-as-you-go pricing
    2. instant scalability
    3. deploy globally with low latency
    4. benefit from lower prices because there are many users
    5. increase speed and agility ; freedom to do things


